author: Tony Doris
title: West Palm Mayor: municipal golf course won't be sold
text:
West Palm Beach Mayor Jeri Muoio says rumors that the city plans to sell, pave over or cut its municipal golf course to nine holes are false.
But the city commission will consider ideas for the courseâ€™s future, which will be presented by consultant RMA at a mayor/commission work session Sept. 8, including the possibility of a public-private partnership, she said.
